claim.claim-text:
14. A method comprising:
determining if a first optical transceiver is connected to a second optical transceiver via an optical link, wherein the first optical transceiver includes an optical transmitter;
if the first optical transceiver is connected to a second optical transceiver via an optical link, connecting a transmit input termination to an electrical input signal to the optical transmitter; and if the first optical transceiver is not connected to a second optical transceiver via an optical link, disconnecting the transmit input termination from the electrical input signal to the optical transmitter.
